# validate-traceability wiring rule

Run `signalos validate-traceability --json` before treating product Beliefs as
source-traced.

- Every product Belief must carry required provenance front matter.
- Every product Belief must appear in `.signalos/TRACEABILITY_MATRIX.md`.
- Source artifacts named in Beliefs and matrix rows must resolve inside the
  workspace.
- Signal threshold, MIN N, and Zone history evidence are mandatory.
